    "text": "I\u2019m so mad because Mandi has a Storage that is under my name and she hasn\u2019t paid the rent for the storage unit this month so they reach out to me\u2026. But what pisses me off as I need to get in that damn Storage and get Cooper\u2019s mattress out and I can\u2019t because she hadn\u2019t paid the rent. \ud83e\udd26\ud83c\udffb\u200d\u2640\ufe0f",
